1202
01:30:27.170 --> 01:30:30.570
Kõik, mis ta tegi,
jäi talle endale.


1203
01:30:31.170 --> 01:30:34.070
Endale? Mitte ainult.

1204
01:30:34.270 --> 01:30:35.970
Hr Mathieu!

1205
01:30:38.570 --> 01:30:40.270
Hr Mathieu!

1206
01:30:42.670 --> 01:30:44.470
Oodake üks hetk.

1207
01:30:47.370 --> 01:30:49.270
Hr Mathieu!

1208
01:30:55.070 --> 01:30:56.470
Mida sina siin teed?

1209
01:30:56.670 --> 01:30:58.970
Võin ma teiega kaasa tulla?

1210
01:30:59.170 --> 01:31:00.470
Härra!

1211
01:31:00.670 --> 01:31:04.470
Ma ei saa. Pead kooli tagasi
minema. Muidu saad karistada.


1212
01:31:04.670 --> 01:31:05.870
Palun.

1213
01:31:05.970 --> 01:31:07.870
Kas tulete juba?
- Kohe.


1214
01:31:08.070 --> 01:31:11.170
Ma ei tohi. Ma ei saa
sind kaasa võtta.


1215
01:31:11.270 --> 01:31:12.870
Mine tagasi.

1216
01:31:13.070 --> 01:31:14.470
Mine!

1217
01:31:15.070 --> 01:31:16.670
Mine!

1218
01:31:42.070 --> 01:31:44.770
Pépinot polnud
asjata lootnud.


1219
